About Us

Following a Rich Tradition Major Rental is a pioneering institution with a rich history and strong tradition. The experience and knowledge we have gained over the years have strengthened our commitment to providing the best service to our customers. Operating as a leader in the industry since the early 2000s, Major Rental has specialized in luxury car rentals. We take pride in having served hundreds of satisfied customers in the past, and we will continue to work with the same dedication in the future. While our fleet consists of the latest technology vehicles in the industry, our team always prioritizes customer satisfaction with our extensive experience and expertise. Each vehicle is meticulously maintained to provide excellent performance and unique comfort. Our roots form the foundation of our focus on customer satisfaction. By always prioritizing quality and excellence, we continue to solidify our position as a leader in the industry as Major Rental. Our past gives us strength and allows us to look to the future with hope. Reach the pinnacle of luxury car rental experience with Major Rental. Every journey you take with us will be an unforgettable experience.
